## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="e1b93-102">一个<xref:System.CodeDom.CodeDefaultValueExpression>可用于表示对默认值的引用。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e1b93-102">A <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeDefaultValueExpression> can be used to represent a reference to a default value.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="e1b93-103"><xref:System.CodeDom.CodeDefaultValueExpression.Type%2A>属性指定对值类型的引用。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e1b93-103">The <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeDefaultValueExpression.Type%2A> property specifies the reference to the value type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="e1b93-104"><xref:System.CodeDom.CodeDefaultValueExpression>类用在基于泛型的代码生成。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e1b93-104">The <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeDefaultValueExpression> class is used in the generation of generics-based code.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="e1b93-105">有关泛型的详细信息，请参阅[.NET Framework 类库中的泛型](~/docs/csharp/programming-guide/generics/generics-in-the-net-framework-class-library.md)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e1b93-105">For more information on generics, see [Generics in the .NET Framework Class Library](~/docs/csharp/programming-guide/generics/generics-in-the-net-framework-class-library.md).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="e1b93-106">若要进一步介绍了使用此部分中提供了以下的代码步骤<xref:System.CodeDom.CodeDefaultValueExpression>类，以将新的默认值添加到代码图。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e1b93-106">The following code steps are provided in this section to further describe the use of the <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeDefaultValueExpression> class to add a new default value to a code graph.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="e1b93-107">第 1 部分中的代码是为提供一个更大示例的一部分<xref:System.CodeDom.CodeTypeParameter>类。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e1b93-107">The code in part 1 is part of a larger example provided for the <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeTypeParameter> class.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="e1b93-108">此代码中，通过 C# 代码生成器，运行时导致出现在第 2 部分中的 C# 代码。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e1b93-108">This code, when run through the C# code generator, results in the C# code that appears in part 2.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="e1b93-109">在第 3 部分中的语句中调用此代码时，结果将是第 4 部分中所示的输出。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e1b93-109">When this code is called in the statement in part 3, the result is the output shown in part 4.</span></span>  
  
```  
// Part 1: Code to create a generic Print method.  
            CodeMemberMethod printMethod = new CodeMemberMethod();  
            CodeTypeParameter sType = new CodeTypeParameter("S");  
            sType.HasConstructorConstraint = true;  
            CodeTypeParameter tType = new CodeTypeParameter("T");  
            sType.HasConstructorConstraint = true;  
  
            printMethod.Name = "Print";  
            printMethod.TypeParameters.Add(sType);  
            printMethod.TypeParameters.Add(tType);  
            printMethod.Statements.Add(ConsoleWriteLineStatement(  
                new CodeDefaultValueExpression(new CodeTypeReference("T"))));  
            printMethod.Statements.Add(ConsoleWriteLineStatement(  
                new CodeDefaultValueExpression(new CodeTypeReference("S"))));  
```  
  
```  
// Part 2: Code generated by code in part 1.  
public virtual void Print<S, T>()  
            where S : new()  
         {  
            Console.WriteLine(default(T));  
            Console.WriteLine(default(S));  
        }  
```  
  
```  
// Part 3: Call to the generated method.  
dict.Print<System.Decimal, int>();  
```  
  
```  
// Part 4: Output of the generated method.  
0  
0  
  
```  
  
   
  
